what's gonna happen to you

07:11.932 --> 07:13.172
if you don't start cooperating?

07:14.735 --> 07:16.535
This is a statement

07:16.537 --> 07:18.036
acknowledging your involvement

07:18.038 --> 07:19.638
in the shooting of Marvin Grant.

07:19.640 --> 07:21.106
Everything in here
has been corroborated

07:21.108 --> 07:22.541
by an eyewitness.

07:22.543 --> 07:24.709
You understand what that means?

07:33.019 --> 07:35.120
