07:35.122 --> 07:36.988
I ain't no killer.

08:14.794 --> 08:16.795
All right, let's go!

08:32.812 --> 08:34.712
- You real cute!
- Put your hands...

08:34.715 --> 08:35.746
St-stand back!

08:41.386 --> 08:42.953
Let's go. Come on.

08:52.799 --> 08:54.799
Kc, phone for you.

08:54.801 --> 08:56.401
I'll call them back, please.

08:56.403 --> 08:58.269
It's something about Colin.

08:58.271 --> 09:00.305
They said it's urgent.

09:02.174 --> 09:04.309
- What's the prisoner's name?
- Colin Warner.

09:04.311 --> 09:05.410
All right.

09:07.313 --> 09:09.948
Uh, nope.
He's been denied bail.

09:10.983 --> 09:12.851
For how long?

09:12.853 --> 09:16.087
Till he goes to trial, unless
the judge rules otherwise.

09:17.423 --> 09:19.791
- All right, thank you.
- Mm-hmm.

09:20.893 --> 09:22.794
I'm sorry, dread.

09:22.796 --> 09:24.763
So, where's my mother?

09:26.198 --> 09:29.434
She had to go to work.

09:29.436 --> 09:31.770
Something with her boss.

09:36.443 --> 09:38.243
You all right, man?

09:39.845 --> 09:42.714
It's fucked up in here.

09:42.716 --> 09:45.917
And no matter what I say,
nobody want to listen to me.

09:45.919 --> 09:49.287
Not even my own mother.

09:49.289 --> 09:52.857
Brethren, the truth
is going to come out.

09:52.859 --> 09:55.827
All right?

09:55.829 --> 09:59.197
Just hang in there
until the trial start.

10:03.937 --> 10:06.104
Them whitey have
killed enough people out there.

10:06.106 --> 10:06.963
Yo, pass that shit!

10:06.988 --> 10:09.307
Y-you're worried about those
shooters in flatbush?

10:09.309 --> 10:10.975
